    "description": "<br><br>Time Titans VR 是一款单人动作射击游戏，允许玩家手动放慢时间以在战斗中获得优势。射击、猛击和切穿敌人，同时减慢时间以发动混乱或闪避反击。 <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/5a3f48026f00c0a84f42031eb094eebe.poster.avif?t=1689855175\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/5a3f48026f00c0a84f42031eb094eebe.webm?t=1689855175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/5a3f48026f00c0a84f42031eb094eebe.mp4?t=1689855175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在自由移动重击对手的同时，按下按钮即可减慢时间。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/3a8e560a389c66561597d0d428d65880.poster.avif?t=1689855175\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/3a8e560a389c66561597d0d428d65880.webm?t=1689855175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/3a8e560a389c66561597d0d428d65880.mp4?t=1689855175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用狼牙棒、战斧、赛斯、剑和其他各种近战武器将你的敌人打成碎片。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/4c87e4f49f04afc027be2f6e67bc1149.poster.avif?t=1689855175\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/4c87e4f49f04afc027be2f6e67bc1149.webm?t=1689855175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/4c87e4f49f04afc027be2f6e67bc1149.mp4?t=1689855175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在慢动作极乐中击败敌人。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/82f6b1fba87aef4669b66391c14560fb.poster.avif?t=1689855175\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/82f6b1fba87aef4669b66391c14560fb.webm?t=1689855175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148110/extras/82f6b1fba87aef4669b66391c14560fb.mp4?t=1689855175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在模拟道德困境时测试你的道德指向，看看你是否值得加入 &quot;公司&quot; 并担任雇佣兵。你的决定将影响故事的进展，并最终决定在经历艰难面试后是否能得到这份工作。 <br><br>你真的适合这份工作吗？ 不妨试一下。",
